Police In Mombasa County Have Recovered The Body Of A Man Suspected That Have Hacked His Wife To Death On Saturday. Peter Mukundi Killed His Wife Ruth Kaveke At Mbuyuni In Likoni, Mombasa County With A Machete Before He Disappeared. Speaking To KTN News On Phone, Likoni OCPD Jane Munyoki Confirmed The Incident Adding That The Body Of The Man Was Found Sunday Morning In A Thicket At Mama Ngina Waterfront. The OCPD Said Police Have Launched Investigations Into The Murder But Believe The Man Was On A Suicide Mission.